Chrono24 GmbH
Haid-und-Neu-Strasse 18, 76131 Karlsruhe, Germany
and
MPN Marketplace Networks GmbH
Haid-und-Neu-Strasse 18, 76131 Karlsruhe, Germany
The companies (hereinafter "Chrono24") can be contacted at:
Email:
info@chrono24.com
Phone: +49 721 96693-0
