This website uses cookies mainly to provide you with an enhanced site navigation by analyzing our site usage and improving your experience. We also make use of cookies for marketing purposes. You have the right to decide which types of cookies you allow us to use. In order to do so, please click on the different category headings to learn more and to set your default settings. In case you would like to change your settings, you can do so by opening our Privacy Preference Center by clicking on the link "Cookie Settings" in the footer of the Website. Please note that blocking some types of cookies may negatively impact your experience on the website and the services we are able to offer. For more information, please visit our
Privacy and Cookie policy.
Always Active
These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some parts of the site will not then work.
Performance Cookies
These cookies allow us to measure and improve the performance of our site by counting visits and traffic sources. They help us to know which pages are the most and least popular and see how visitors move around the site. All information these cookies collect is aggregated and therefore anonymous. If you do not allow these cookies we will not know when you have visited our site, and will not be able to monitor its performance.
Analytics cookies
Analytics cookies are used to track your behavior and activity on this website by improving the overall user experience. These cookies allow us to understand better how you interact with the website by informing us about the content you have consulted, any errors you might have encountered and the duration of your session on the site.
Advertising Cookies
These cookies are used to track your browsing activities and behavior on our website in order for us to deliver relevant information and advertisements on other websites. These cookies are generally set through our site by our advertising partners, with our permission. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising.
Functional Cookies
These cookies enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and personalisation and help us remember certain of your choices (e.g. language, region etc.). They may be set by us or by third party providers whose services we have added to our pages. If you do not allow these cookies then some or all of these services may not function properly.
