Riskified may jointly use personal data in accordance with procedures permitted by law to the extent needed to carry out our business operations, as detailed in this Privacy Policy, including but not limited to the uses listed under the title above ‚ÄúUse of Collected Information‚Äù. When we jointly utilize personal information with other companies, we are hereby providing notice of the following.
